#

Roasted Red Pepper Soup

40 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

main

Tags:

soupcomfort foodeasy meal

Description

A creamy and vibrant soup bursting with the rich flavors of roasted red peppers, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • roasted red peppers: 2 cups
  • vegetable broth: 3 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • basil: 1 tablespoon, fresh (optional)
